              "isPermaLink": "false"
            },
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/?p=38372"
          },
          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>開拓動漫官方公開，「ASCA ASIA TOUR 2025」將於10月18日在台北舉辦。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/38372\">「ASCA ASIA TOUR 2025」將於10月18日在台北舉辦</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">開拓動漫官方公開，「ASCA ASIA TOUR 2025」將於10月18日在台北舉辦。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"993\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19210335/2025ascaasiatourtaipeiprologue01-1024x993.webp\" alt=\"2025ascaasiatourtaipeiprologue01\" class=\"wp-image-38373\" title=\"「ASCA ASIA TOUR 2025」將於10月18日在台北舉辦 6\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19210335/2025ascaasiatourtaipeiprologue01-1024x993.webp 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19210335/2025ascaasiatourtaipeiprologue01-300x291.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19210335/2025ascaasiatourtaipeiprologue01-768x745.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19210335/2025ascaasiatourtaipeiprologue01-1536x1490.webp 1536w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19210335/2025ascaasiatourtaipeiprologue01-750x727.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19210335/2025ascaasiatourtaipeiprologue01-1140x1106.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19210335/2025ascaasiatourtaipeiprologue01.webp 1653w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">預定參演「ANISAMA WORLD 2025 in TAOYUAN」的歌手「ASCA」，曾演唱過《刀劍神域 Alicization》片頭曲「RESISTER」、《皇帝聖印戰記》片尾曲「PLEDGE」、《艾梅洛閣下II世事件簿 -魔眼蒐集列車 Grace note-》片尾曲「雲雀」、遊戲《鳴潮》1.3主題曲「Never Let It Go」，如今確定單獨以「ASCA」舉辦亞洲巡迴活動。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「ASCA ASIA TOUR 2025」將於10月18日在台北舉辦，更多詳情將於日後公開。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.f-2.com.tw/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.f-2.com.tw/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">開拓動漫官網</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/38372\">「ASCA ASIA TOUR 2025」將於10月18日在台北舉辦</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "post-id": {
            "_attributes": {
              "xmlns": "com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"
            },
            "_text": "38372"
          }
        },
        {
          "title": {
            "_text": "「NATIVE x 豬帽子 成人向特展」於豬帽子西門形象店開設中"
          },
          "link": {
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/38365"
          },
          "dc:creator": {
            "_cdata": "萌朧雪猴"
          },
          "pubDate": {
            "_text": "Sun, 18 May 2025 16:19:07 +0000"
          },
          "category": [
            {
              "_cdata": "活動新訊/報導"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "紳士向"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "紳士模型"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "美少女模型"
            }
          ],
          "guid": {
            "_attributes": {
              "isPermaLink": "false"
            },
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/?p=38365"
          },
          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>專營日本動漫玩具零售、GSC認證合作販售店鋪、野獸國認證授權經銷商，於全台有六間直營實體門市的「豬帽子」，宣布攜手日本模型品牌「NATIVE」，於豬帽子西門形象店舉辦「NATIVE x 豬帽子 成人向18禁特展」，除展出模型外亦規劃展覽活動。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/38365\">「NATIVE x 豬帽子 成人向特展」於豬帽子西門形象店開設中</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">專營日本動漫玩具零售、GSC認證合作販售店鋪、野獸國認證授權經銷商，於全台有六間直營實體門市的「豬帽子」，宣布攜手日本模型品牌「NATIVE」，於豬帽子西門形象店舉辦「NATIVE x 豬帽子 成人向18禁特展」，除展出模型外亦規劃展覽活動。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"743\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19000810/2025mayBoarhattwnativenews01-743x1024.webp\" alt=\"2025mayBoarhattwnativenews01\" class=\"wp-image-38366\" style=\"width:1170px;height:auto\" title=\"「NATIVE x 豬帽子 成人向特展」於豬帽子西門形象店開設中 7\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19000810/2025mayBoarhattwnativenews01-743x1024.webp 743w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19000810/2025mayBoarhattwnativenews01-218x300.webp 218w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19000810/2025mayBoarhattwnativenews01-768x1058.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19000810/2025mayBoarhattwnativenews01-1115x1536.webp 1115w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19000810/2025mayBoarhattwnativenews01-750x1034.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19000810/2025mayBoarhattwnativenews01-1140x1571.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/19000810/2025mayBoarhattwnativenews01.webp 1486w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 743px) 100vw, 743px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">豬帽子表示現場將展出「NATIVE」紳士向精美模型，另外還會有兩個展覽活動：</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">購買任一NATIVE商品，即贈限定小禮物乙份。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">購買任一NATIVE商品，即可獲得已展出模型抽獎資格。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">(於2025/07/04(五)20:00粉絲專頁直播線上抽獎，抽取5名中獎者。)</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">※活動僅限於豬帽子西門形象店</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「NATIVE x 豬帽子 成人向18禁特展」，自2025年5月17日開展至6月29日。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「NATIVE x 豬帽子 成人向18禁特展」展覽資訊</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">展覽時間：2025/05/17(六) &#8211; 06/29(日)</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">展覽地點：豬帽子西門形象店 | 台北市萬華區武昌街二段85號之5</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">【注意事項】</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">1.本展覽為18禁展覽，入場請攜帶身份證明證件以供年齡查驗，未滿18歲者禁止入場。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">2.活動贈品數量有限，每日限量發放，數量以實際贈送數量為主；贈品不得轉換、轉讓或折換現金，如遇瑕疵恕不更換。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">3.中獎者請攜帶對獎聯至西門形象店領獎，抽獎券若遺失恕不補發。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">4.凡參與本活動即接受活動注意事項及相關規定，本公司可修正、暫停或終止活動，並保有最終解釋即決定之權力。 </p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Boarhat.tw/?locale=zh_TW\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/Boarhat.tw/?locale=zh_TW\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">豬帽子FB</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/38365\">「NATIVE x 豬帽子 成人向特展」於豬帽子西門形象店開設中</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
